metadata.name: NYCE #1
metadata.description:
A rare digital collection granting ownership to NYCE’s NYCE Coin logo.  
Utility: With only 2500 in existence, the NFT grants access to TRIBE U, as well as an exclusive token-only Telegram group with unique NYCE content.  
As NYCE and the TRIBE grow, so may the token’s resale value.  
- Rare ownership of NYCE’s NYCE Coin logo  
- Verified TRIBE U member ($279 value)  
- Telegram group with exclusive wealth-building content  
- 100+ wealth-building courses by self-made millionaires
